# {{ project_name_title }} — Claude Code Context

## Stack

- Python 3.12, Poetry
- Streamlit frontend
- jackknife for LLM, memory, and data tooling

## Commands

```bash
# Install
poetry install

# Run the app
poetry run streamlit run main.py

# Run tests
poetry run pytest

# Lint + format
poetry run ruff check . --fix
poetry run ruff format .
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── main.py           # Streamlit entry point
├── pyproject.toml
├── .env.example      # Required environment variables
└── tests/
```

## Environment

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in your secrets.
Never commit `.env` to version control.
